{"tid":910430,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[大艦巨根主義] 俾斯麥號沉沒","createTime":"2018-11-21T07:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T16:23:52.000Z","uid":18679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"989f2665b7a9650a96498d94dcbf70cd32711e47","tid":910430,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"二戰入面其中一個最引人入勝既戰役<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcpcmd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvcpcmd6.png&h=02ff86fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月24日朝早五點幾打到5月27日11點幾<br />\n<br />\n打沉英Flagship Hood, 打到Prince of Wales半傷<br />\n<br />\nHood 全員1418人，救返3個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOVyP7C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOVyP7C.png&h=6f6805b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBismarck 比人打到漏油仲要快過你架King George V<br />\n<br />\n追追下成架Bismarck 都唔見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔左15個鐘終於知道Bismarck 去緊法國<br />\n<br />\n26號美國女機師Smith終於locate到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLdD1ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLdD1ec.png&h=867154d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係知道又點 無咩艦又夠快又夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後都係要靠航母Ark Royal d 魚雷機先打到Bismarck 1/3血<br />\n<br />\n之後27號朝早英艦4隻圍住Bismarck黎屌 出動埋16吋巨根屌足成朝先搞掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但Bismarck都未沉 補多兩支魚雷先搞掂<br />\n<br />\n最後希特拉總結 大艦巨炮都係玩唔過<br />\n1- 太貴<br />\n2- 對空太弱<br />\n3- 太食油<br />\n4- 輸左會太樣衰 打擊士氣<br />\n<br />\n你又點睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCP7UzD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCP7UzD.png&h=ba71e4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Sink the Bismarck!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"38cf56580d5322dbe5eebf79a0facd602b3ba848","tid":910430,"uid":18679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2CV1tvMYFRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2CV1tvMYFRs&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=85573353\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2CV1tvMYFRs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kz8pmbytxoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKz8pmbytxoQ&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=873f77ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kz8pmbytxoQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OJeI5_9c29s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOJeI5_9c29s&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c2ff6d0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OJeI5_9c29s</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cV0NNZbj2QI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcV0NNZbj2QI&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7836d79d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cV0NNZbj2QI</a><br />\n<br />\n精彩外國animation總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2399d1d3155041679d5d3a2062389fd512ee488","tid":910430,"uid":18679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"16吋巨根用炮彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wf3D1gD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWf3D1gD.png&h=d3319ffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f5a6395a8be4a167f7dd33b419842bfecc8c569","tid":910430,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ba